album.title: Dancing with the Devil: The Art of Starting Over

wiki.summary: "Met Him Last Night" is the ninth track from Demi Lovato's seventh studio album, Dancing with the Devil…The Art of Starting Over (2021). It was released on April 2, 2021 through Island Records. It's the first collaboration between Lovato and Ariana Grande. “I remember playing ‘Dancing With the Devil’ for Ariana back in 2019 when I was at her concert in London. We were backstage and she was so excited. She's always been super supportive of me and my career, and it's so awesome to have a friend like her in the industry. Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: "Met Him Last Night" is the ninth track from Demi Lovato's seventh studio album, Dancing with the Devil…The Art of Starting Over (2021). It was released on April 2, 2021 through Island Records. It's the first collaboration between Lovato and Ariana Grande. “I remember playing ‘Dancing With the Devil’ for Ariana back in 2019 when I was at her concert in London. We were backstage and she was so excited. She's always been super supportive of me and my career, and it's so awesome to have a friend like her in the industry. She started writing this song and immediately thought of me, so when she gave it to me I was like, ‘We should just sing this together.’” -- Demi Lovato Read more on Last.fm.
